sm', 'Carisoprodol, Orphenadrine, Baclofen, Cyclobenzaprine, Methocarbamol, Chlormezanone', 'Vincristine, Cabazitaxel, Vinblastine, Paclitaxel, Topotecan, Teniposide, Irinotecan, Vinorelbine, Etoposide, Docetaxel', 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/64460/', '[1] "Product Information. Yondelis (trabectedin)." Janssen Pharmaceuticals, Titusville, NJ.[2] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[3] "Product Information. Yondelis (trabectedin)." Janssen Pharmaceuticals, Titusville, NJ.[4] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0', 1767369485);
